Organization Name: TARRANT COUNTY PUBLIC HEALTH | DR. MARION J. BROOKS PUBLIC HEALTH BUILDING | COMMUNITY HEALTH NAVIGATION
Keywords: Social Services, Comprehensive Information and Referral
Description: Provides assistance to clients with enrollment in the following programs and services: Affordable Care Act - Federally-Facilitated Marketplace Medicare, Medicaid Children's Health Insurance Plan (CHIP), Healthy Texas Women, JPS Connection, Baylor Scott & White Health Plan, local health clinics, SNAP Food Benefits, TANF, and WIC.
